quran[11{c,v,t}:
19,1,"kaaf, hay, y, a, s"
19,2,zikar hai uss rehmat ka jo tairay rab ne apne bande Zikria par ki thi
19,3,jabkay uss ne apne rab ko chupkay chupkay puraka
19,4,"uss ne arz kya"" ae parvar-digaar, meri haddiyan taq ghul gayi hain aur sir burhapay se bharak utha hai ae parvar-digaar, mein kabhi tujh se dua maang kar namuraad nahi raha"
19,5,"mujhe apne peechay apne bhai bundon ki buraiyon ka khauf hai, aur meri biwi banjh hai to mujhe apne fzlِ khaas se aik waris ataa kar day"
19,6,"jo mera waris bhi ho aur aalِ Yaqoob ki meeras bhi paye, aur ae parvar-digaar, uss ko aik pasandeeda ensaan bana """
19,7,"( jawab diya gaya )"" ae Zikria, hum tujhe aik larke ki basharat dete hain jis ka naam yahya ho ga hum ne iss naam ka koi aadmi is se pehlay peda nahi kya """
19,8,"arz kya,"" parvar-digaar, bhala mere haan kaisay beta hoga jabkay meri biwi banjh hai aur mein boorha ho kar sookh chuka hon? """
19,9,"jawab mila"" aisa hi ho ga tera rab farmata hai ke yeh to mere liye aik zara si baat hai, aakhir is se pehlay mein tujhe peda kar chuka hon jab ke to koi cheez nah tha """
19,10,"Zikria ne kaha,"" parvar-digaar, mere liye koi nishani muqarrar kar day"" farmaya"" tairay liye nishani yeh hai ke to pihm teen din logon se baat nah kar sakay """
19,11,chunancha woh maharab se nikal kar apni qoum ke samnay aaya aur is ne isharay se un ko hadaayat ki ke subah o shaam tasbeeh karo
